item.description: Hi! I’m Nicholas. I’m a Software Engineering student at the University of Waterloo. I have experience in frontend and backend development from my time working at Rivalry. I have also worked on projects such as a messaging web app , a multiplayer chess app , and wearable glasses that assist in playing blackjack. Aside from school, I spend my time making origami and playing piano which have been long-standing passions of mine.
